sequenceDiagram
    title 時序圖 2/7 — 獲取控制租約
    %% 說明：Operator 選擇車輛後，建立 Session + 取得 ControlLease（30分鐘 TTL），
    %%       再向 LiveKit 請求 operator role 的 Room Token。
    %% 流程：選擇車輛 → POST sessions → 建立 Session
    %%       → POST control-lease/claim（pg_advisory_lock 防重入）→ 建立 Lease
    %%       → POST livekit/token → 簽發 LiveKit JWT（含 roomJoin + canPublish + canSubscribe）

    participant O as "操作員\nOperator"
    participant CP as "Web Cockpit\n(Next.js 3011)"
    participant API as "Backend API\n(Next.js 3010)"
    participant DB as "PostgreSQL\nDatabase"
    participant LK as "LiveKit SFU\n(v1.7.2)"

    O->>CP: 選擇車輛「AMR-01」
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/vehicles/vehicle-001/sessions
    API->>DB: 建立 Session (ACTIVE)
    DB-->>API: Session Created
    API-->>CP: sessionId
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/vehicles/vehicle-001/control-lease/claim
    API->>API: pg_advisory_xact_lock(vehicle-001)
    API->>DB: 查詢現有 ACTIVE Lease
    DB-->>API: 無衝突
    API->>DB: 建立 ControlLease (ACTIVE, 30min TTL)
    DB-->>API: Lease Created
    API-->>CP: Lease Claimed
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/livekit/token
    API->>API: 簽發 LiveKit Token (role: operator)
    API-->>CP: LiveKit Token + Room 資訊
